1
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:58,000
Dragon Princess.

2
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:00,800
Long time no see.

3
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:04,959
Di Yun.

4
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:06,240
Your jade pendant.

5
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:07,000
I fixed it.

6
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,340
Here, take it back.

7
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,260
You actually fixed it?

8
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:11,720
Miss.

9
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,840
What else do you want?

10
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:14,320
Miss,

11
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,740
may I ask your name?

12
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:16,960
I want to thank you.

13
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:17,960
No need.

14
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,940
I broke your pendant earlier.

15
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,760
I am truly sorry.

16
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,880
But now that it is fixed,

17
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:23,280
I do not owe you anything.

18
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,200
Wait.

19
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:26,970
This pendant...

20
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,720
it was forged from a Celestial artifact.

21
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:29,920
How did you fix it?

22
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:35,840
Miss!

23
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:36,600
Miss!

24
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:41,720
Did she use up all her spiritual energy

25
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:43,080
just to fix my pendant?

26
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,640
For a thousand years,

27
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:57,240
no one has ever done so much for me.

28
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,360
I told you, I don't owe you anything.

29
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,880
We are strangers now. Let's never meet again.

30
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:13,360
Hey!

31
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,360
You are Ling'er, right?

32
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,090
I heard Qingluan call you that.

33
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,360
If you won't tell me,

34
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,920
I will call you that from now on.

35
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:22,180
What is wrong with you?

36
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:29,410
Ling'er.

37
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,650
Ling'er!

38
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,400
I am already home.

39
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,600
Why are you still following me?

40
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,200
Ling'er...

41
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:35,640
I...

42
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,440
I just want you by my side.

43
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,460
"He would rather wander the world

44
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,480
than go back for the marriage alliance."

45
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:43,320
You...

46
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,760
Yueying was right.

47
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:45,960
You really are a dissolute man.

48
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,960
Next you are going to say, "I like you,"

49
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,020
"marry me," right?

50
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,040
No, Ling'er.

51
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:50,520
You...

52
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,000
I...

53
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,400
Little Highness.

54
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,760
You are swinging your hoe

55
00:02:58,760 --> 00:03:00,480
a bit too eagerly.

56
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:02,880
You have dug your way to my doorstep.

57
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,320
King Kunmi.

58
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,210
Look at what you are saying.

59
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,680
People who do not know better

60
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,680
might think I am trying to steal your lover.

61
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,560
You rogue!

62
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,890
I am not anyone's lover!

63
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,440
Ling'er and I are in love.

64
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:15,720
Little Highness,

65
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,320
wasn't what you just said

66
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,960
a bit out of line?

67
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,930
When was I ever in love with you?

68
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:22,320
Forget it.

69
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,560
I will deal with this annoyance first.

70
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,160
King Kunmi runs hot and cold,

71
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:27,820
but at least he is a gentleman.

72
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,240
That is right.

73
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,840
Yunyuan and I are in love.

74
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,120
So just give up.

75
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:39,840
As far as I know,

76
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,460
King Kunmi remains unmarried

77
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,960
because he is devoted to the Dragon Princess who has slept for a thousand years.

78
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:48,480
The world says King Kunmi is a devoted lover.

79
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,680
Could it be

80
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,600
that the rumors of your devotion are false?

81
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:53,530
Ling'er.

82
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,000
You are too naive.

83
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,600
Don't be fooled by this player.

84
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,760
So you have an old flame.

85
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:01,570
Ling'er.

86
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,860
It's not like that.

87
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,240
You're asking for a beating.

88
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:09,960
Look, Ling'er.

89
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,090
He is getting angry.

90
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:32,480
Is this a duel between the mighty ones?

91
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,720
How exciting.

92
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,100
Look, Ling'er.

93
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:37,200
I hit a nerve.

94
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:38,320
This man is unreliable.

95
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,200
Stay at my manor.

96
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,320
I am much more reliable than him.

97
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:42,320
But he looks more reliable than you.

98
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,280
Noisy.

99
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,560
Brother.

100
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,580
Your Highness.

101
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,960
Why are they fighting?

102
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:51,240
Di Yun said something,

103
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,770
and your brother got angry.

104
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:55,210
What could possibly anger my brother?

105
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:58,020
Your sunflower seeds smell good.

106
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,640
Oh.

107
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:05,120
So someone got jealous.

108
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,160
Brother.

109
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:07,480
Take it easy.

110
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,280
Don't destroy the place.

111
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:09,080
Your Highness.

112
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,320
You take it easy, too.

113
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,960
If you break anything, I'll make you pay for it.

114
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,480
Why did they stop?

115
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,360
Right.

116
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,560
Why did they stop?

117
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,240
Di Yun.

118
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,160
Ling'er is mine.

119
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,600
Just because you say so?

120
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,120
You are betrothed.

121
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:29,360
I already broke off the engagement.

122
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,040
Sister Qingluan.

123
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,680
I remember you saying

124
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:35,520
the Heavenly Emperor's son came here to escape a marriage.

125
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:36,000
Yunyuan.

126
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:38,960
He just said you were waiting for a sleeping Dragon Princess.

127
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:39,520
Di Yun.

128
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,640
Your engagement is also to a Dragon Princess.

129
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,560
So the two of you

130
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,760
have been love rivals all along.

131
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,640
I really am a genius.

132
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,400
Let's go.

133
00:05:58,840 --> 00:05:59,760
I don't believe it.

134
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,920
You keep dragging her around

135
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,120
and won't let her out.

136
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:07,440
(Sighs)

137
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:10,680
Ling'er.

138
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,560
What is wrong?

139
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,720
Why are you sighing?

140
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,200
That annoying Di Yun.

141
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:16,000
I don't know what's gotten into him.

142
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,960
Whenever I go out now,

143
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:17,960
he pesters me.

144
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,600
Now I don't even dare to leave the house.

145
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,960
Do you have a way

146
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,400
to drive him away?

147
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,760
Didn't Brother fight him the other day?

148
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,080
He still dares to pester you?

149
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:27,880
I'm wondering the same thing.

150
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,240
Yunyuan already said we are in love.

151
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,840
Why won't he give up?

152
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,180
Brother really said that?

153
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,000
Then I do have a plan.

154
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,880
What plan?

155
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:43,280
With my sworn brother as your backer,

156
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:45,050
who else would you ask for help?

157
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,159
But...

158
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,730
doesn't he already have someone he likes?

159
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,840
That wouldn't be right.

160
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:52,240
What goes on in that little head of yours?

161
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:52,960
Trust me.

162
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,490
He'll definitely help you.

163
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,120
I promise.

164
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,159
But...

165
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:58,280
If you have a problem, go to my sworn brother.

166
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,520
He'll fix it.

167
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:00,520
Sister Qingluan.

168
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,160
Dear God,

169
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:22,600
please send me a handsome and useful husband.

170
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:28,080
Are you that desperate for a man?

171
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,720
Why are you here?

172
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,760
This is my manor.

173
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,520
Why wouldn't I be here?

174
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,160
Then could you let go of me first?

175
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,200
And if I don't?

176
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,160
What will you do?

177
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,480
I'm really sorry about earlier.

178
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,560
I accidentally made you fall into the water.

179
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,490
Why don't you...

180
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,090
go change your clothes?

181
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,520
What?

182
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,960
You don't need to change?

183
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,480
Or...

184
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,320
do you want to go out like that for everyone to see?

185
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,640
Every time I see him,

186
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,200
he seems to be unwell.

187
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,919
Now that I made him fall into the water,

188
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,280
will he get sick?

189
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,200
If he gets sick because of me,

190
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:43,679
I'll owe him another debt.

191
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,520
I'm in good health.

192
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,760
I don't have any hidden illnesses.

193
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,480
You...

194
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,740
How do you know what I'm thinking?

195
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:53,090
You haven't answered my question.

196
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,600
Are you that desperate for a man?

197
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,000
No.

198
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,080
By the way, Yun Yuan.

199
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,320
Here in your Yunshen Manor,

200
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,280
is there anyone...

201
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,600
both talented and handsome,

202
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,130
who is also willing to help?

203
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,010
Talented and handsome?

204
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,520
There is someone.

205
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,560
Then can you call him out

206
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,480
to do me a favor?

207
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,160
I'll make it up to him.

208
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:24,640
Look at me.

209
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,280
Do I look like that person,

210
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,420
who is talented and handsome?

211
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:31,480
You?

212
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,880
No way.

213
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:40,400
You are talented and handsome,

214
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,360
but with that face of yours,

215
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,400
no matter how I look at it,

216
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:45,460
you don't look like someone helpful.

217
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,620
What am I thinking?

218
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:22,280
How could I lust after King Kunmi?

219
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:23,480
What do I do?

220
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:29,160
I don't seem to mind him being this close.

221
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,160
I'm done for.

222
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,130
I'm really done for.

223
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:07,320
You've been wandering around Yunshen Manor for a while.

224
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:09,180
Haven't you seen anyone you like?

225
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,880
This outfit is quite nice.

226
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:17,360
Didn't you leave this at my door, Sister?

227
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:22,920
By the way,

228
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,920
what kind of man are you looking for exactly?

229
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:25,920
At the very least,

230
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,960
he has to be better looking than Di Yun.

231
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,760
Otherwise, if I take him out,

232
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,090
Di Yun won't believe it.

233
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:31,800
Strange.

234
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:34,080
Why am I thinking of Yunyuan?

235
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:37,280
He's better looking than Di Yun.

236
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:39,080
You should have said so earlier.

237
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,770
Where are you taking me?

238
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:41,680
To find...

239
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,600
...someone even better looking than Di Yun.

240
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,400
Brother.

241
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,530
Brother, are you there?

242
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:47,880
Sister Qingluan.

243
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,560
Aren't we going to find someone more handsome than Di Yun?

244
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:52,280
Why are we looking for your brother?

245
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:54,600
To find someone more handsome than Di Yun...

246
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,040
...it has to be my brother.

247
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:56,840
My brother...

248
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,930
...is handsome, fit, and capable.

249
00:11:58,960 --> 00:11:59,800
Compared to that Di Yun...

250
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:01,660
...he completely outshines him.

251
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,400
Brother.

252
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,360
Brother.

253
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,160
What is it?

254
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:09,640
Brother.

255
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,560
Ling'er.

256
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:12,640
She needs your help with something.

257
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:15,600
Can't I just stay in Yunshenbuzhichu?

258
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,240
So awkward.

259
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,800
Um...

260
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,040
It's nothing, never mind.

261
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:23,170
Sorry to bother you.

262
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,680
Don't be like that.

263
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:25,880
If you don't say it...

264
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:27,140
...I'll say it for you.

265
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:27,960
Brother.

266
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,840
Ling'er wants to know if you have time recently...

267
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,200
...to pretend to be her beloved...

268
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,930
...and help her drive away that pestering Di Yun.

269
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,200
Understood.

270
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,120
You agreed?

271
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:40,960
Let's do it tomorrow.

272
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,080
Tomorrow...

273
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,920
...we can go for a walk together.

274
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:44,720
Okay.

275
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,360
Tomorrow it is.

276
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,840
You have no idea.

277
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,300
Lately, to avoid Di Yun...

278
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,960
...she hasn't stepped a foot outside.

279
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:53,040
Mushrooms are about to grow on her head.

280
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:54,160
It's fungi.

281
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,520
Whatever you say.

282
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,800
That's more like it.

283
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:06,340
Stern for a thousand years, and finally an expression.

284
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:09,160
It seems only the one who tied the bell can untie it.

285
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:16,000
Our Ling'er is so beautiful.

286
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:18,480
You're the most beautiful, Sister.

287
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,740
You little flatterer.

288
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,600
Sister.

289
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:24,800
How fortunate...

290
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:27,200
...to have met you in Kunmi City.

291
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,120
Yes.

292
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,480
How fortunate...

293
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,720
...in Kunmi City...

294
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:32,900
...to have met you.

295
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:36,680
Otherwise, if Brother couldn't find you...

296
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:38,140
...he would have gone mad.

297
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:47,560
Brother.

298
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,370
I'm leaving Ling'er in your hands.

299
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:57,440
Sister Qingluan.

300
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,500
Aren't you coming?

301
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,520
I...

302
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:00,560
...have something to do.

303
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:01,560
So I won't go.

304
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,600
Have fun.

305
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,480
Sister Qingluan.

306
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:09,850
Let's go.

307
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,050
Ling'er.

308
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,160
You came out.

309
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,560
Where do you want to go today?

310
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:14,400
I'm sorry.

311
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:16,880
I have plans to go out with Yunyuan today.

312
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:20,200
See that? I'm taken.

313
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,680
Stop pestering me.

314
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,200
Then I'll come along.

315
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,520
I'm a guest from afar.

316
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:25,200
King Kunmi,

317
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,360
surely you know how to treat a guest?

318
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:28,560
Treat a guest?

319
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:32,720
Ling'er,

320
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,160
let's go.

321
00:14:34,760 --> 00:14:35,360
Yunyuan,

322
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:35,890
let's go.

323
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:44,080
Aren't we being a bit too intimate?

324
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:46,480
If we're going to put on a show,

325
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,960
we have to go all the way.

326
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:48,800
Right?

327
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:51,640
Ling'er?

328
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:53,760
So mushy.

329
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:54,880
I like it.

330
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:56,050
Ling'er,

331
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:56,960
the flowers on West Mountain are blooming.

332
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,000
Let's go see them.

333
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,130
Ling'er,

334
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:01,480
let's go to East River to see the flowers.

335
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:03,880
Forget East River. Let's go to West Mountain.

336
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:04,600
East River.

337
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:05,660
West Mountain.

338
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:11,690
General.

339
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:12,480
Speak.

340
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,320
Lightning tribulation struck.

341
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,680
A snake demon is wreaking havoc again.

342
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:17,940
The villagers nearby have all suffered.

343
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:23,960
Lightning tribulation?

344
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:24,880
A snake demon?

345
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:28,160
Evacuate the villagers.

346
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:30,840
Take a squad of elites and kill it on the spot.

347
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,120
I've already arranged people

348
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:33,920
to treat the injured villagers.

349
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:35,160
But...

350
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,120
What is it?

351
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:38,600
The snake demon is cunning.

352
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:40,330
We couldn't find its true body.

353
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:45,480
I'll go myself.

354
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:47,040
Tell Qingluan

355
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,160
to handle the aftermath properly.

356
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,290
Humans are fragile.

357
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,360
Bring more herbs.

358
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,320
Yes, sir.

359
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,480
You?

360
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:37,820
I chased a shadow here.

361
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:38,800
Did you see it?

362
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:39,800
No.

363
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:42,520
Did you see a demonic snake?

364
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:44,560
That's what I'm chasing.

365
00:16:44,760 --> 00:16:45,960
You were probably chasing

366
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:47,440
just one of its clones.

367
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:48,280
Ah.

368
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:50,120
King Kunmi.

369
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,000
Don't steal my prey.

370
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,000
Stay out of my way.

371
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:25,339
If I hadn't been asked to help,

372
00:17:25,359 --> 00:17:26,640
I wouldn't bother with you.
